metadata.name: Birth of the World
metadata.description:
This NFT represents the Original Canvas Painting I did in 2020.
It is a gift to my 1/1 collectors for Christmas 2022.
Editions of 2.

100x60 cm (39x24 inch)
Oil on canvas
2020

A child comes into this world full of creatures and objects unknown to him. What everything looks like and what everything is intended for is yet to be discovered. 

The world is kind to the newborn being, mysterious and fabulous. The infant itself is safe, in petals of a flower, in an unopened bud.
